          "title": "EVA [https://github.com/georgia-tech-db/eva]",
          "summary": "EVA is a database system for building simpler and faster AI-powered applications. EVA is designed for supporting database applications that operate on both structured (tables, feature vectors) and unstructured data (videos, podcasts, PDFs, etc.) using deep learning models. It also supports an AI-oriented SQL-like query language tailored for analyzing unstructured data.",
